hopobject.body: Beaglebone robotics platform with two DC motors controlled by and L298 dual motor controller one Parallax standard servo and a custom circuit board with a user button, piezoelectric buzzer, and a TXB0108 level shifter that sits on the expansion headers.
hopobject.shortdesc: Work in progress beaglebone robotics platform designed for the MICS 2012 robotics competition.
